Whos this male prostitute-looking kid?
I am the matchless Ha Hu-Yeong, the greatest martial artist reigning over all the lands! There is no one that is my equal! I was drowning in futility and emptiness because there was no more that I could accomplish in the human realm. To reach the peak of martial arts, I must become a saint! However, the other saints refused my ascension due to my karma after much slaughter, and I fell, just like that.
When I woke up, I was 60 years in the future. I was reborn as the second lord of the Namgung family: Namgung Hyuk. Where has all the internal energy that Ive accumulated gone?! Moreover, I have the Nine yin energy blockage?
(Source: Kakao, translated and edited)

Yu-Jin is an F-ranker overshadowed by his little brother, an S-ranker. All he does is get in his brothers way, causing trouble wherever he goes. When a seemingly routine dungeon raid goes wrong and costs Yu-Jin his brothers life, Yu-Jin decides to use the wish granted by clearing the dungeon to reset his timeline. The plan was to lead a quiet life from now on but now it turns out he can help other people become S-rankers?! Maybe this is Yu-Jin's chance at building his own entourage of powerful metahumans but it may be easier said than done.
(Source: WEBTOONS, edited)
